msgctxt "0000"
msgid "So... Misko's treasure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0001"
msgid "I...see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Deal!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "No way!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk00"
msgid "<1.so>Prissen! Hang on!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I've got the scoop on Misko's <2.se_co>treasure<3.re_co>,\n"
"and it's great! Listen up, Dak..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk02"
msgid "<1.so>Prissen! You're going to give it all away!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk03"
msgid "<1.so>Sorry, Dak... <2.pa>I got carried away."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Anyway, we're busy here, dude.\n"
"If you need something, take it up\n"
"with someone else."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: choice
msgctxt "Talk05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You again? Pay no mind to my little bro's\n"
"chatter from before. He's got a penchant\n"
"for running his mouth with crazy talk.<2.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ahhh shoot. Welp. Can't say I didn't try\n"
"to throw him off..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: text_size
#. 3: text_size
msgctxt "Talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Anyway. Misko's treasure—not that we\n"
"were talking about such a thing—is only\n"
"for the BEST of treasure hunters. \n"
"That probably rules you out, bub.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<2.te_si>The fewer people after it, the better.\n"
"And we've still got the scoop!<3.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, Dak... Why don't we just tell him?\n"
"Maybe he'll leave us alone if we do.\n"
"\n"
"I mean, if we can't figure this riddle out,\n"
"there's no way someone like him will be\n"
"able to."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>...That's a good point.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk10"
msgid "<1.so>Heh.<2.pa> Good deal."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well, I've got nothing to say to some\n"
"bum without even two rupees to rub\n"
"together."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk12"
msgid "<1.so>Way to go, Dak. You did it!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Misko hid the location of the treasure in\n"
"some kind of strange secret code.\n"
"\n"
"I heard this from a former dog walker of\n"
"one of Misko's underling's descendant's\n"
"neighbors. As solid a lead as any."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Just knowing someone with good intel\n"
"like that? Exactly what I'd expect from\n"
"you, Dak!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>But this riddle has even I, Domidak,\n"
"the premier treasure hunter,\n"
"scratching my head.\n"
"<2.so>So that you can tell how challenging my\n"
"work is, <3.pa>I'll tell it to you. <4.pa>You'll never\n"
"solve it, though."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk16"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The little twin steps over the little river.\n"
"My cave rests above that river's source."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: pause (long)
#. 7: choice
msgctxt "Talk17"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It'll be <2.se_co>100 rupees<3.re_co> to learn what\n"
"we know.\n"
"\n"
"Truth is, it'd be a steal to get this\n"
"exclusive scoop for <4.se_co>1,000 rupees<5.re_co>...<6.pa>\n"
"So what do you say?<7.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk18"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hey, buddy! What's your problem?<2.pa> You\n"
"aren't being incredibly rude and listening\n"
"to our conversation, are you?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (red)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk19"
msgid ""
"<1.so>We're treasure hunters, on the trail of\n"
"our latest score... The<2.se_co> treasure of the\n"
"great bandit Misko<3.re_co>!<4.pa> It's as good as ours!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk20"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That's the keen sense of the strongest\n"
"treasure hunter at work! No gold left\n"
"behind—not by Domidak!\n"
"You're great, Dak!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.pa>We're after nothing less than the\n"
"<3.se_co>treasure of Misko, the Great Bandit<4.re_co>!\n"
"Finding it would mean incredible riches...\n"
"I'm not about to give this information\n"
"away for free. I'm no fool!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "near00"
msgid "<1.so>Hrm..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "near01"
msgid "<1.so>I bet it's over there!"
msgstr ""

